{"tid":1888212,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如何才能確診武漢肺炎？","createTime":"2020-02-20T05:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T02:38:03.000Z","uid":76310,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4910fb5d31463f6e114e7323ac53677ace8396","tid":1888212,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"如何才能確診武漢肺炎？<br />\n<br />\n1.需要有齊武漢肺炎所有病徵<br />\n2.需要官方認可醫生確認<br />\n3.需要官方認可醫院確認<br />\n4.需要使用官方認可的檢測方法下確診<br />\n5.需在十四天內發病<br />\n6.需要發燒高於38度<br />\n7.需要在官方指定隔離地點十四天內發病<br />\n8.需要確認與確診者有直接接觸<br />\n9.不能有其他病<br />\n<br />\nn. 即使有齊以上徵狀條件 如果中央政府不承認你有武漢肺炎 你就沒有確診"},{"pid":"b2d2267e36efd7e5805e2f525ad67cd5637f05a7","tid":1888212,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589661b3f990f4522d109300b51f3334a4663368","tid":1888212,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:16:25.000Z","msg":"去報個失先"},{"pid":"21ef322a23ab56c2463dcab2183264cdf6988e0c","tid":1888212,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:16:41.000Z","msg":"三個字:支那人，無辜的，沒一個。請自行重組句子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b027fd57e9104f5055c51e1dd369449cd17ecb7","tid":1888212,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992006fbd73e21838365d850e39f47f2884731b0","tid":1888212,"uid":104106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:38:03.000Z","msg":"到時沒確診就唔撥落死亡數字<br />\n<br />\n中國又贏"}]}